attributionInfo.brokerName: Keller Williams Realty Boston-Metro | Back Bay

description: A stunning loft-style condo in the heart of Boston’s sought-after Seaport/Fort Point neighborhood. This beautifully updated home features a modern kitchen and bathroom, blending contemporary finishes with the charm of exposed brick and beam architecture. The recently renovated kitchen boasts sleek quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample storage, making it perfect for cooking and entertaining. The updated bathroom offers a Kohler cast iron tub, elegant tile work, and high-end fixtures. There are two beds, a queen-sized Murphy bed, and a king-size bed, in the loft space above the kitchen, which can also double as storage. Enjoy the convenience of extremely low HOA fees and the rare benefit of an assigned parking space, providing stress-free city living. Just steps away from trendy restaurants, shopping, and the Seaport waterfront. Don’t miss this opportunity to own a move-in-ready condo with modern upgrades and unbeatable convenience! Schedule a showing today!
